    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a set of scenarios in which complications when identifying which policy to apply for a host are encountered. This problem is abstracted as "host identification". Describing these scenarios allows commonalities between scenarios to be identified, which is helpful during the solution design phase.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document does not include any solution-specific discussions.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
